{"tid":493313,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"猁狗串撚到","createTime":"2017-12-08T11:34:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T05:10:01.000Z","uid":94771,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87acbc3fd8392bcb68d436e1fe705406aef54504","tid":493313,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=XOwmgkNIqoyGEiS1u1KBVZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=f0b7f318\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】看到利物浦於歐聯以7:0血洗莫斯科斯巴達的強勁氣勢後，愛華頓球迷難免會為下周日上演的默西賽德打吡擔心，紅軍球迷則意氣風發。<br />\n<br />\n默西賽德打吡將於周日頭場上演，利物浦要拉近與榜首曼城之間的距離，就要趁曼市打吡曼城有機會失分的同時，球隊必須要全取3分。雖然愛華頓最近漸入佳境，周四也在歐霸贏波，不過眼見利物浦的強勁氣勢和決心，愛華頓球迷都認為就算是艾拿戴斯領軍，都未必阻止到對方大開殺戒。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而球迷在twitter上的留言，亦都一面倒認為愛華頓今仗凶多吉少。網民@olami_suasik說，「今個周末愛華頓想要一個怎樣的葬禮？」@gerrardbella說，「我只能說，RIP愛華頓」，紅軍球迷@ginge_lfc_5說，「愛華頓你是下一個目標。」另一利迷@Agyei93說，「我不認為愛華頓會逃得過被我們大炒。」</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n小心輸翻轉頭比人恥笑好個啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f61cf451994a28b672d590e10c454f62c21062","tid":493313,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:38:13.000Z","msg":"等有魔性嘅牙朗收佢地皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2041343158b44eac43fcc09714b012ecb093440b","tid":493313,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:44:14.000Z","msg":"倫敦打吡：潮撐韋斯咸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n默郡打吡：潮撐利記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n曼市打吡：潮撐曼城<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aa91a71340fae749020e830d67ec7f2b5d9e39b","tid":493313,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-08T11:59:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce623bfa24b37d9e61cc129332ea021dcc9b86a6","tid":493313,"uid":51951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB